WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:06.301
Every month, the books have to close. And every month, skilled people give up their nights to get there.

00:06.501 --> 00:14.254
Across the industry, closing the month takes six point four days on the median, and that number has barely moved in fifteen years.

00:14.454 --> 00:20.250
Three out of four accountants have had to reopen the books, to fix an error found after the close.

00:20.450 --> 00:26.678
Ninety nine percent report burnout. And three hundred thousand have left the profession in just two years.

00:26.878 --> 00:29.256
It isn't the people. It's the work.

00:29.456 --> 00:40.164
Sophon Finance Systems builds finance engines that absorb the mechanical month: drafting the entries, tying every schedule to the ledger, and citing every figure to its source.

00:40.364 --> 00:48.465
Our public demo close runs in fifteen hundredths of a second, and every run is checked by an independent verifier that never gets tired.

00:48.665 --> 00:57.726
Machines do the work. Your people keep the judgment, and the final signature. Sophon Finance Systems. Automate the work. Keep the judgment.

